snippet.title: MOB Review: Soul Gambler
snippet.description:
Soul Gambler is a story driven choice experience on Steam here: 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/313020/

Join us at Twitter or Facebook if that is your thing:
https://twitter.com/TheSocioPsycho
https://www.facebook.com/pages/Sociopsycho/708973969124737?ref_type=bookmark

Please thumbs up and share the video if you are feeling generous, 
or thumbs down if you did not like it, and tell us why, thank you for your viewership and constant support!

MOB= My observed buttle

My channel is dedicated to bring you reviews on PC games done in a professional manner, where you can see the game for what it is, good or bad and make a decision based of what you hear and see.
For more videos check out the channel at http://www.youtube.com/user/SocioPyscho

Because this is a review with my commentary it is protected under the fair use law because it is for critical and educational purposes. It is fair use and does not violate any of YouTube's Policies or Terms of Service. This means that I can use this gameplay footage as long as I provide commentary that is somewhat educational or instructional without the copyright owners consent."

End music is royalty free by Teknoaxe 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtgf00GvfFQVsYBA7V7RwUw
